      ],
      "notes": "<p>A small Digimon with feline traits. Always whimsical, Nyaromon received its name for its cat-like behavior. While curious and fickle by equal measures, it has a lonely side as well. It uses its special move Fox Tail to whip the enemy with the wiry hairs on its tail. Not a single foe has ever been seen flinching under this attack.</p>"
